results.name: Second differences of A000219.
reference: G. Almkvist, The differences of the number of plane partitions, Manuscript, circa 1991.
formula: a(n) ~ 2^(13/36) * Zeta(3)^(31/36) * exp(1/12 + 3*Zeta(3)^(1/3)*n^(2/3)/2^(2/3)) / (A * sqrt(3*Pi) * n^(49/36)), where Zeta(3) = A002117 and A = A074962 is the Glaisher-Kinkelin constant. - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Oct 30 2016
mathematica: nmax = 50; Drop[CoefficientList[Series[(1-x)^2 * Product[1/(1-x^k)^k, {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x], 2] (* _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Oct 30 2016 *)
